UPHENDUKE undabizekwayo umshado okusabalele ivideo yawo ezinkundleni zokuxhumana, kubatshazwa ukudelela kowesilisa obephikisana nomfundisi ngezifungo. Kule video kuvela lo wesilisa oqophisana nomfundisi okumele asho amazwi emva kwakhe. Kwezinye izifundo uvele afune zeqiwe atshele umfundisi ukuthi kade badlula kulokho. Uma ebuzwa ukuthi uzomthanda yini kukuhle noma kukubi, uvele athi akabuze umakoti. Uphinde abuzwe ukuthi uzomthanda yini uma bempofu noma becebile, aphendule ngokuthi bampofu vele. Umfundisi uzwakala etshela umkhwenyana ukuthi uyazonela umshado wakhe, umkhwenyana aphendule ngokuthi uyamncikiselela.   Kuze kungenelele owesifazane ofike ancenge umkhwenyana embiza ngoNyambose, abhoke ngolala umkhwenyana. Uvele akhombise ukungalaleli, axoshe lo wesifazane ukuthi akahlale phansi. Umfundisi ugcine esethi akudlulelwe kumakoti ngesikhathi sekubabaza bonke abantu umkhwenyana ethi ngeke akuqinisekise ukuthi ngeke bahlukane nomakoti uma endindile (egagula igama elisetshenziswa kowesifazane ongaziphethe kahle). Ezinkundleni zokuxhumana abantu bebebabaza ukuhlazeka kuka makoti abanye bezibuza ukuthi kungani engasho lutho ekubeni umyeni wakhe ephuma emgqeni. Okuthuse abantu kakhulu nokho ukuthi lo mshado uqhubekile: